{"type": "article", "id": 16160, "title": "Layer 手链", "description": "", "date": "2015-10-16T06:50:15Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 46, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702125737KZlAHc0wbYW2qXfn.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t这条手腕带可以采集“碳足迹（carbon footprints）”，即我们呼出的二氧化碳，并连上手机 app，来自英国伦敦的设计事务所 Layer。设计的灵感源于我们对健身消耗的记录，可以帮助使用者分析日常习惯，选择更健康的居住环境。不过，带彩色圆点的石制手链本身就很独特了。<a href=\"http://layerdesign.com/projects/worldbeing/\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里可以查看更多信息。</a>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726143523J8hCD6FpvdSzfGgi.jpg\" width=\"600\" height=\"409\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.68166667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726143523U8xl2gSvaAEZFt0p.jpg\" width=\"600\" height=\"409\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.68166667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726143523lTuNwbL9UHM7hy8V.jpg\" width=\"600\" height=\"275\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.45833333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726143524RzjD7tIaCvf9wgh0.jpg\" width=\"600\" height=\"320\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.53333333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n"}